'''2015年巴加大屠殺'''，是指2015年1月3日至1月7日的五天時間內，[[博科聖地|博科聖地]]在[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]][[巴加鎮_(奈及利亞)|巴加鎮]]（或譯巴嘎、巴格等）發生的[[大屠殺|大屠殺]]事件。[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]1月9日稱，博科聖地在攻下該鎮後，殺了包括老弱婦孺在內的2000名[[平民|平民]]<ref>{{cite news|author=周虹汶(譯)|title=博科聖地殺兩千人 倖存者踩屍逃難|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/846444|accessdate=2015-01-11|newspaper=[[自由時報|自由時報]]|date=2015-01-11|archive-date=2015-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113135825/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/846444|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年1月3日，博科聖地擊潰了由[[乍得|乍得]]、[[尼日尔|尼日尔]]、[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]組成的{{link-en|多國聯合特遣部隊|Multinational Joint Task Force}}，[[佔領|佔領]]位於巴加鎮內的{{link-en|奈及利亞陸軍|Nigerian Army}}基地後，便開始進行了無差別的大屠殺，一直殺到7日。事後傷亡報告已確定為「嚴重」，但人數還未完全確認。當地官員引述逃離的居民的證言稱，有超過2000人被殺或下落不明，而其他的報告則指出至少100人死於大屠殺<ref name=AFP_BI /><ref name=BBC_1>{{cite news|title=Boko Haram crisis: Nigeria's Baga town hit by new assault|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-30728158|accessdate=8 January 2015|work=[[BBC_World_News|BBC World News]]|agency=[[British_Broadcasting_Corporation|British Broadcasting Corporation]]|date=8 January 2015|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617161931/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-30728158|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=NBC_News>{{cite news|last1=Smith|first1=Alexander|title=Boko Haram Torches Nigerian Town of Baga; 2,000 Missing: Senator|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/missing-nigeria-schoolgirls/boko-haram-torches-nigerian-town-baga-2-000-missing-senator-n282291|accessdate=8 January 2015|work=[[NBC_News|NBC News]]|agency=[[National_Broadcasting_Company|National Broadcasting Company]]|date=8 January 2015|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612221258/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/missing-nigeria-schoolgirls/boko-haram-torches-nigerian-town-baga-2-000-missing-senator-n282291|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Reuters_1>{{cite news|title=Boko Haram kills dozens in fresh raids in Nigerian town|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2015/01/08/uk-nigeria-violence-toll-idUKKBN0KH1QD20150108|accessdate=8 January 2015|agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|publisher=[[Thomson_Reuters|Thomson Reuters]]|date=8 January 2015|archive-date=2015-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708231338/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2015/01/08/uk-nigeria-violence-toll-idUKKBN0KH1QD20150108|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

但奈及利亞的政府官員則駁斥了當地官員的說法。稱死亡人數沒有當地官員與國際媒體說的這麼多，或稱大屠殺從未發生，奈及利亞軍隊已經擊退了博科聖地的武裝分子。<ref name=Sun_1 /><ref name=News_Express_1 /><ref name=NBC_News />

據報導，巴加與至少其他16個城鎮已被摧毀，超過3萬5千人流離失所，有許多人因試圖穿越[[邊境|邊境]]逃難，而困在[[乍得湖|乍得湖]]與附近的[[小島|小島]]<ref name=AFP_BI /><ref name=Reuters_1 />。博科聖地一系列的襲擊，已經攻下[[博尔诺州|博尔诺州]]70%的土地。<ref name=BBC_1 />

== 背景 ==
{{main|在奈及利亞的叛亂}}
巴加位於[[博尔诺州|博尔诺州]]，是{{link-en|奈及利亞陸軍|Nigerian Army}}基地與{{link-en|多國聯合特遣部隊|Multinational Joint Task Force}}（Multinational Joint Task Force，MNJTF）總部的所在地。多國聯合特遣部隊是由[[乍得|乍得]]、[[尼日尔|尼日尔]]、[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]為了跨國境的安全問題，於1994年成立，最近的行動則是打擊博科聖地的叛亂分子。<ref name=News_Express_1 /><ref name=AFP_BI>{{cite news|title=Boko Haram destroys at least 16 villages in NE Nigeria: officials|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/afp-boko-haram-destroys-at-least-16-villages-in-ne-nigeria-officials-2015-1|accessdate=8 January 2015|work=Business Insider|agency=[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]]|date=8 January 2015|archive-date=2018-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180401115140/http://www.businessinsider.com/afp-boko-haram-destroys-at-least-16-villages-in-ne-nigeria-officials-2015-1|dead-url=no}}</ref> 因此，該鎮對博科聖地而言具有戰略意義，也是{{link-en|奈及利亞政治|Politics of Nigeria|奈及利亞政府}}在其所控制下的博尔诺州北部，與多國部隊的一個關鍵軍事基地。<ref name=AFP_BI />

== 大屠殺與襲擊 ==
攻擊開始於1月3日，一支[[博科聖地|博科聖地]]的大部隊[[佔領|佔領]]了巴加鎮，與鎮內的陸軍基地，及聯合特遣部隊總部。<ref name=NBC_News_2>{{cite news|last1=Smith|first1=Alexander|title=Boko Haram Militants in Nigeria Storm Key Base in Baga|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/missing-nigeria-schoolgirls/boko-haram-militants-nigeria-storm-key-base-baga-n279731|accessdate=8 January 2015|work=[[NBC_News|NBC News]]|publisher=[[National_Broadcasting_Company|National Broadcasting Company]]|date=8 January 2015|archive-date=2018-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180330012538/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/missing-nigeria-schoolgirls/boko-haram-militants-nigeria-storm-key-base-baga-n279731|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===襲擊聯合特遣部隊總部===
根據博尔诺州中央區{{link-en|參議員 (奈及利亞)|Senate (Nigeria)|參議員}}{{link-en|艾哈迈德·赞纳|Ahmed Zanna}}的說法，當時唯一駐紮的政府軍是奈及利亞陸軍，儘管軍隊曾抵抗過來自四面八方的武裝份子對指揮部的攻擊，但幾個小時後，政府軍最終「加入平民，逃往叢林中」。<ref name=NBC_News_2 /><ref name=LWJ_1>{{cite news|last1=Roggio|first1=Bill|title=Boko Haram overruns Multinational Joint Task Force base|url=http://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2015/01/boko_haram_overruns_1.php#ixzz3OGgsjjEN|accessdate=8 January 2015|work=[[Long_War_Journal|Long War Journal]]|date=4 January 2015|archive-date=2017-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816063028/http://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2015/01/boko_haram_overruns_1.php#ixzz3OGgsjjEN|dead-url=no}}</ref> Zanna還對記者說，這支博科聖地的大部隊也因此獲得武器與車輛。

同日，博科聖地的武裝分子開始強行進入巴加鎮與周圍村落的民家。<ref name=NBC_News />1月6日晚上，兩名當地居民向記者說，武裝分子使用[[汽油彈|汽油彈]]與[[炸藥|炸藥]]破壞建築物，並殺害倖存者。<ref name=NBC_News /><ref name=Reuters_1 /> 1月9日，居民向記者說，當地房子已經被破壞到沒有一間完好。<ref name=WSJ_1>{{cite news|last1=Hinshaw|first1=Drew|last2=Akingbule|first2=Gbenga|title=Boko Haram Rampages, Slaughters in Northeast Nigeria|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/boko-haram-rampages-slaughters-in-northeast-nigeria-1420816770|accessdate=10 January 2015|work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]|publisher=Dow Jones & Company|date=9 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111034921/http://www.wsj.com/articles/boko-haram-rampages-slaughters-in-northeast-nigeria-1420816770|dead-url=no}}</ref>當地區政府與{{link-en|庫卡瓦鎮|Kukawa}}的負責人Musa Bukar則稱，當地的16座村莊均被夷為平地，居民不是被殺就是逃難。<ref name=AFP_BI />

=== 死亡人數 ===
關於死亡的確切人數，各方報導並不一致。 Bukar說超過2000人已經被殺<ref name=BBC_1 />，Zanna堅稱這2000人是「下落不明」 ，但其他報導有一百到數百人不等。<ref name=Reuters_1 /><ref name=NBC_News /> 區長Baba Abba Hassan則稱，有100人是在1月3日被殺，但之後他又補充說，有數百具[[屍體|屍體]]仍躺在街頭，其中包括了被武裝分子追上的婦女和小孩。<ref name=Reuters_1 /><ref name=Sun_1>{{cite news|last1=Olanrewaju|first1=Timothy|title=One week after Boko Haram attack, corpses litter Baga|url=http://sunnewsonline.com/new/?p=99371|accessdate=9 January 2015|work=The Sun (Nigeria)|date=9 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115140459/http://sunnewsonline.com/new/?p=99371|dead-url=no}}</ref> 然而Hassan否認了1月7日曾經發生襲擊的消息，並稱2000人死亡的數字相當離譜。
<ref name=Sun_1 /> 奈及利亞政府也否認了有大量傷亡的說法，稱死亡人數是相當低的。<ref name=Vice_News_1>{{cite news|last1=Hayden|first1=Sally|title=Gruesome Reports Emerge of New Boko Haram Massacre in Northern Nigeria|url=https://news.vice.com/article/gruesome-reports-emerge-of-new-boko-haram-massacre-in-northern-nigeria|accessdate=9 January 2015|work=[[Vice_News|Vice News]]|publisher=[[Vice_Media|Vice Media]]|date=8 January 2015|quote=''However, an NGO researcher in Nigeria told VICE News that she had heard from various sources — including one inside the Ministry of Defence — that the number of new fatalities in Baga could be considerably lower, though she couldn't independently confirm those claims.''|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108200116/https://news.vice.com/article/gruesome-reports-emerge-of-new-boko-haram-massacre-in-northern-nigeria|archive-date=2015-01-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 不過奈及利亞政府在過去就有多次淡化或否認受到博科聖地襲擊的紀錄，包括了博科聖地分子與{{link-en|奈及利亞軍|Nigerian Armed Forces|政府軍}}均涉入其中的{{link-en|2013年巴加大屠殺|2013 Baga massacre}}，是場屠殺造成超過200名平民死亡。<ref name=Al-Jazeera_1>{{cite news|title=Boko Haram seizes strategic Nigerian town :Boko Haram seizes strategic Nigerian town Army denies takeover even as thousands of people are reported fleeing northern Nigerian town amid Boko Haram attack.|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2014/09/boko-haram-seize-strategic-nigerian-town-201492185035408733.html|accessdate=9 January 2015|work=[[Al_Jazeera_English|Al Jazeera English]]|publisher=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]|date=2 September 2014|quote=''Boko Haram have seized a strategic town in Nigeria's far northeast, prompting denials from the military... [which] countered that it had pushed back the militants, who in recent weeks have moved from indiscriminate and retaliatory hit-and-run attacks to seizing strategic territory in Borno state.''|archive-date=2015-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110201021/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2014/09/boko-haram-seize-strategic-nigerian-town-201492185035408733.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CBS_1>{{cite news|title=Nigeria gov't denies new Boko Haram mass kidnap|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/nigeria-denies-boko-haram-kidnapped-another-60-girls-31-boys/|accessdate=9 January 2015|work=[[CBS_News|CBS News]]|publisher=[[Columbia_Broadcasting_System|Columbia Broadcasting System]]|date=24 June 2014|quote=''Witnesses say Islamic extremists have abducted 60 more girls and women and 31 boys from villages in northeast Nigeria. Security forces denied the kidnappings.''|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109234050/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/nigeria-denies-boko-haram-kidnapped-another-60-girls-31-boys/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Daily_Trust_1>{{cite news|last1=Bello|first1=Usman A.|title=Police Deny Boko Haram Attack in Kogi|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201409170864.html|accessdate=9 January 2015|work=Daily Trust|agency=AllAfrica|date=17 September 2014|quote=''The police in Kogi State yesterday refuted reports of an attack on a military vehicle by suspected Boko Haram members in the state.''|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109235659/http://allafrica.com/stories/201409170864.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 事後各方反應 ==
政府的安全官員很快地駁斥了在巴加有任何攻擊的說法，並稱：「在基地的部隊守住了他們的陣地。」 <ref name=News_Express_1>{{cite news|title=Boko Haram suffers heavy defeat in surprise attack on military base|url=http://www.newsexpressngr.com/news/detail.php?news=8954&title=Boko-Haram-suffers-heavy-defeat-in-surprise-attack-on-military-base|accessdate=9 January 2015|work=News Express|date=5 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807072724/http://www.newsexpressngr.com/news/detail.php?news=8954&title=Boko-Haram-suffers-heavy-defeat-in-surprise-attack-on-military-base|archive-date=2017-08-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>當地一家親政府的報紙引述一名漁夫的話，稱巴加鎮正牢牢處於政府軍控制之下，博科聖地的攻擊結果是「慘敗」。<ref name=News_Express_1 /> [[空軍元帥|空軍元帥]]兼{{link-en|國防總參謀長 (奈及利亞)|Chief of the Defence Staff|國防總參謀長}}的{{link-en|亚历克斯·巴德|Alex Badeh}}在最初否認MNJTF總部已被佔領，但之後承認。<ref name=News_Express_2>{{cite news|title=Boko Haram displaces 1,636 in Baga|url=http://www.newsexpressngr.com/news/detail.php?news=8995&title=Boko-Haram-displaces-1,636-in-Baga-(Borno)|accessdate=9 January 2015|work=News Express|date=7 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150605034028/http://www.newsexpressngr.com/news/detail.php?news=8995&title=Boko-Haram-displaces-1,636-in-Baga-(Borno)|archive-date=2015-06-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=AP_1>{{cite news|last1=Adigun|first1=Bashir|title=Nigerian Defense Chief: Military Base in Hands of Extremists|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/nigerian-defense-chief-military-base-hands-extremists-28026238|accessdate=9 January 2015|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]]|date=6 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109182700/http://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/nigerian-defense-chief-military-base-hands-extremists-28026238|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

一位政府發言人給了籠統的不準確數字，稱有1636人逃難<ref name=News_Express_2 />；但根據其他報導和當地官員的說法，則是至少有3萬5千人逃離該地<ref name=BBC_1 />。倖存者稱，「屍體散布街頭」，巴加鎮的全部人都已經逃離，有的進入[[喀麦隆|喀麦隆]]和[[乍得|乍得]]。<ref name=Reuters_1 /><ref name=LWJ_1 />大約有20,000人在[[邁杜古里|邁杜古里]]附近的營地尋求庇護，有1萬人逃到州的首府{{link-en|蒙古諾|Monguno}}等待運輸。<ref name=AFP_BI /><ref name=BBC_1 /> Bukar說，巴加鎮幾乎已不存在。  <ref name=BBC_1 /> 當地的[[人權活動家|人權活動家]]稱，他們被告知有逃離該鎮的婦女被[[綁架|綁架]]，其中最小的年僅10歲。<ref name=Reuters_1 />

[[乍得总理|乍得总理]][[帕伊米·德贝|帕伊米·德贝]]稱，至少有2,500{{link-en|奈及利亞人|Nigerians}}和500乍得人因為攻擊，試圖使用[[獨木舟|獨木舟]]穿越[[乍得湖|乍得湖]]到達鄰國尋求庇護。<ref name=Reuters_1 /><ref name=NBC_News />大部分的人可能會淹死，而一則報導則指有超過500人被困在湖周圍的小島。<ref name=NBC_News_2 /><ref name=AFP_BI />根據和難民通過電話的當地官員稱，這些在島上的難民飢寒交迫，且因蚊子出沒，很可能死於[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]。 <ref name=Reuters_1 /> 

前州長，現任該州北區參議員的{{link-en|迈纳·马吉·拉万|Maina Maaji Lawan}},則質疑為何士兵從基地逃走。他說：「每次我軍面對博科聖地的襲擊，都從崗位逃離，這肯定是錯誤的。」<ref name=LWJ_1 />這次戰鬥是奈及利亞政府軍在與博科聖地近百次戰鬥時逃跑的其中一次。<ref name=LWJ_1 /> Lawan說，博科聖地已經襲擊了博爾諾州的70%土地，並取得控制權。<ref name=BBC_1 />

